designs embodied in this software are the subject of one or more pending patent
applications, including but not limited to:

  - U.S. Provisional Patent Application No. 63/987,398
    "SYSTEMS AND METHODS FOR BLOCK-SCALE-FREE HIGH-RADIX FLOATING-POINT
    PROCESSING WITH EXPLICIT MANTISSA AND NATIVE LEXICOGRAPHICAL
    COMPARABILITY" (filed February 20, 2026)

